                        <interp inst="t18670128-252-verdict-1" type="verdictSubcategory" value="no_subcategory"></interp>GUILTY</rs>
                  </hi>.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Metcalfe and Hogwood were further charged with having been before con<lb></lb>victed, Metcalfe, at Newington, in the name of <persName id="t18670128-name-312">
