                     </persName>, to which the prisoners</hi> 
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">PLEADED GUILTY</hi>. <hi rend="largeCaps">METCALFE</hi>**—<rs id="t18670128-252-punishment-57" type="punishmentDescription">
